data.eml:eml: Redescription of Trichogrammatoidea annulata De Santis (Hymenoptera: Trichogrammatidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Querino, R. B., Zucchi, R. A. (2004): Redescription of Trichogrammatoidea annulata De Santis (Hymenoptera: Trichogrammatidae). Zootaxa 677: 1-7, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.158556
